asset.title: ARIES Jeep® Wrangler: Modular Front Bumper
asset.description:
This video demonstrates the installation of the ARIES 2071022 Jeep® Modular Front Bumper kit.  These modular bumpers are available in both carbon steel with a textured black powder coat finish, and aluminum in the same textured finish, as well as a silver powder coat.

Features Include:
Six configurations in carbon steel
Ten configurations in aluminum
Durable T6 Aluminum Alloy
Allows for additional lighting
Universal winch housing with 10,000 lb. capacity

Vehicle Coverage:
2007-2015 Jeep® Wrangler 2 Door & 4 Door
